  "keyFeatures": [
    "Enterprise-grade multi-agent orchestration",
    "Production-ready Agent class with memory, tools, and structured outputs",
    "10+ built-in multi-agent architectures (Sequential, Concurrent, MixtureOfAgents, HierarchicalSwarm, etc.)",
    "Universal SwarmRouter for dynamic swarm selection",
    "Agent Orchestration Protocol (AOP) for distributed agent deployment",
    "Model Context Protocol (MCP) integration",
    "CLI tools for agent and swarm management",
    "AutoSwarmBuilder for automatic agent generation",
    "Extensive tool integration and marketplace",
    "Support for all major LLM providers (OpenAI, Anthropic, Groq, etc.)"
  ],
